  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK891">
<l>āṟṟuvā rāṟṟa likaḻāmai pōṟṟuvār</l> 
<l>pōṟṟalu ḷellān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to disregard the power of those who can carry out (their wishes) is more important than all the watchfulness of those who guard (themselves against evil).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
